I was being plagued by a telemarketer that I kept on blocking their number, and he kept getting a new number to plague me again and again and again... so I downloaded this and punked him with it for an hour and a half until he managed to get a text through for me to "please stop".    I had it set to hang up 2 seconds after pickup and redial 1 second after hang up, pretty much rendering his phone useless.    Best dollar I've spent all year!
